# AutoGrader
## Installation
Requirements:
- Python
- `virtualenv` or `venv`

Use the following commands to setup the environment:
- `virtualenv -p $(which python3) .venv`
- `source .venv/bin/activate`
- `pip install -r requirements.txt`
